front.title: •••Combat Cloud Car
front.gametext: Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. At cloud sectors, power and maneuver +1, may deploy as a 'react' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter.
front.lore: Enclosed Ubrikkian Talon I Combat Cloud Car. Speeds up to 1,875 kph. Exceptional maneuverability makes this a favorite of outer Rim security forces.
